page.title: 04Canvey - Transport
page.content: Most of the transport that comes through our area are cars, they come in different shapes and sizes. The most popular cars that I see are Cortinas and the Escorts.There are two main types of buses the double decker bus and the coach.The coach is the most popular out of the two.There is normally about half an hour gap between each bus, that comes. The two taxi services are trio, the A.B.C. and Steve's every day there is normally a few vans about.The most common van is the industrial van but there are others such as the post office van, plumbers van and the builders van.
